headline: U.S. Hospitals Report Lower Clinician Turnover, Aon Reports
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON) reports that more U.S. hospitals are reporting steady or lower employee turnover after bolstering pay and benefits to help attract and retain talent, according to the firm's 19th annual Benefits Survey of Hospitals.
